---

This project incorporates a number of third-party components, each retaining
its original license:

* MinHook (https://github.com/TsudaKageyu/minhook) — MIT, fetched via CMake
  FetchContent at build time.
* Rust crates listed in Cargo.lock — see their respective licenses in
  https://crates.io.

The repository started as a from-scratch reimplementation inspired by
hdrover/discord-drover. No code from that project is included verbatim;
the on-disk configuration format (`drover.ini`) is intentionally compatible.
